Wait for already-started animation preload
==========================================

Date: 2026-07-02

Purpose
-------
Fix the remaining first-seconds GIF stutter after the blocking preload change.

The scaling path can call preload_animation() from resize(), which starts a
background preload and marks the AnimatedImage as already started. Playback
startup then calls preload_animation(block=True), but the previous implementation
returned immediately when preload had already started. That meant the timer could
still begin while scaled frames were being generated.

This change makes block=True wait for an existing preload worker to finish.

